# Docker 
## Build 
```
docker build -t mini-dns .
```
## Run
```
docker run --rm \
    --user "$(id -u)":"$(id -g)" \
    -e USER=$USER \
    -v "$PWD":/usr/src/mini-dns \
    -w /usr/src/mini-dns \
    -p 5546:5546/udp \
    -it mini-dns \
    /bin/bash
```

